Startup

ROM -> RAM
bootloader
system kernel
mem check 
init process
    sets sys states
    login
        sets uid, gid
        starts /etc/passwd startup application

System Start
    startup.py
    login.py
        interpreter.py
            STUFF            
    shutdown.py

