| | --------------------------- | |
| ------------------------------- |              
-----------------------------------

/etc/passwd (: delimited)
---------------------------------------------------------
| username      |                                       |
| password      | random length encrypted (if not 'x')  |
| uid           |                                       |
| gid           |                                       |
| text info     | name, dept, etc (optional fields)     |
| login dir     |                                       |
| startup app   |                                       |
---------------------------------------------------------


